00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:26,980
=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:29,940
=Episode 14=

19
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,480
Your Highness, please give her a hand.

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,840
It's improper for me to do that.

21
00:01:39,190 --> 00:01:40,030
What're you afraid of?

22
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:41,480
I won't tell Xiao Xun'er.

23
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,600
I can handle it myself.

24
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:45,190
I won't burden you guys.

25
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:46,910
By yourself,

26
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:48,080
when can we arrive at the Academy?

27
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,400
No time to waste.

28
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,820
(Jia Nan Academy)

29
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:06,880
Wu Hao.

30
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:10,950
Bai Cheng,

31
00:02:11,550 --> 00:02:12,390
you're back.

32
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,030
How did Bai Shan die?

33
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:23,720
That's how things unfolded.

34
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,110
After the competition,

35
00:02:26,270 --> 00:02:27,630
Elder Hao tried his best to cure Bai Shan.

36
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:29,360
Although he stayed alive,

37
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,720
his meridians were damaged

38
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,960
by the elixirs he had taken

39
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:34,270
due to the corrosivity of elixirs.

40
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,670
His Dou Qi regressed to elementary levels

41
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:39,750
with little chance of advancement.

42
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,830
Elementary levels…

43
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:47,630
That's the same as killing him.

44
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,030
He refused to accept the reality

45
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:50,870
at the beginning.

46
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,670
So, he locked himself in the training room,

47
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:55,000
practicing relentlessly day and night.

48
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,960
Countless posts were broken.

49
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:59,270
But, not being protected by Dou Qi,

50
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,190
he exposed his life to danger

51
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,470
if he kept training himself like that.

52
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,720
That's why he gave me Great Rift Rock,

53
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,750
the skill of your Bai Family,

54
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,600
in the hope of me defeating Xiao Yan.

55
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:11,870
That's to say,

56
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,520
he was deceived by Han Feng at that time.

57
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,160
Yes.

58
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:19,800
He didn't betray us,

59
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,830
nor did he have a way out.

60
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,800
A glimmer of hope, though fake,

61
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,630
was what he wanted to seize.

62
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:32,520
Brother, things have settled down.

63
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,880
Don't think it this way.

64
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,190
Tell me what am I supposed to think?

65
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,750
He has been competitive since childhood.

66
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,440
He was always the best.

67
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:48,080
Xiao Yan crippled his Dou Qi in public,

68
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,030
forcing him to death.

69
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,520
Becoming a traitor

70
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,550
was the wrong path he chose.

71
00:03:56,390 --> 00:03:58,600
But he didn't choose it deliberately.

72
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,960
It's all because of Xiao Yan.

73
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:03,470
I've never considered him a traitor.

74
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:08,390
He did his best to recover his Dou Qi,

75
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,750
and stepped out at the critical moment

76
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:13,600
against the trick of Han Feng.

77
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,550
He was brave for not yielding to failure,

78
00:04:17,110 --> 00:04:18,760
for admitting mistakes and making amends,

79
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:22,230
and for fighting strong enemies head-on.

80
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,200
You should feel proud

81
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,040
of your younger brother.

82
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,600
Sure,

83
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:38,790
I'm proud of him.

84
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,670
He never lowered his head in submission,

85
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:45,040
not even till death.

86
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,790
Xiao Yan!

87
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,000
Keep going. The Academy is up ahead.

88
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,270
With it, you won't keep your head down.

89
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,350
I'm afraid

90
00:05:46,230 --> 00:05:47,920
I might stir up trouble in the Academy again

91
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,510
if I go there.

92
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,790
I hate repeating the past.

93
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,720
Woeful Poison Body is not a cage,

94
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,390
but your inborn gift.

95
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,160
Don't be afraid. Trust me.

96
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,160
The elders would help you.

97
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:16,020
(Jia Nan Academy)

98
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,230
So,

99
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,160
these elixirs…

100
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,280
Again, again.

101
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:21,440
… can not only

102
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:24,720
support Dou Qi practice,

103
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,040
but also play an integral role

104
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:30,000
in real fights.

105
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:32,200
They matter to your lives.

106
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,670
Can any of you

107
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,640
review for us

108
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,640
the functions of elixirs?

109
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,320
He or she will be awarded

110
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,440
the Foundation Building Liquid.

111
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:46,920
What crap liquid.

112
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,390
All you have are useless elixirs.

113
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,440
You!

114
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:53,470
What do you mean?

115
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,320
A load of crap.

116
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,880
Everyone knows

117
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,390
you allow Xiao Yan

118
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,950
to take Fallen Heart Flame for his own use.

119
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:00,790
The Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower

120
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:01,920
is an ordinary pavilion now,

121
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,440
useless for practicing.

122
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,110
Yeah. I agree.

123
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,440
Who told you that?

124
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,560
All rumors.

125
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,550
We came here to improve our Dou Qi.

126
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,110
With no Heavenly Flames,

127
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,320
what's the point of staying here?

128
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,600
Let's all go home.

129
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,000
Yeah. Let's go home.

130
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,840
Go home.

131
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:17,040
Go, go, go. Go back home. Let's go.

132
00:07:17,230 --> 00:07:18,110
Respect class disciplines!

133
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,110
Stop.

134
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,440
- You!
- Wu Hao.

135
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,830
Elder, they disrespect teachers
and disturb the class.

136
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,950
We shouldn't just sit by.

137
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,790
That's not their fault.

138
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:33,070
It's because of Bai Cheng.

139
00:07:36,550 --> 00:07:39,070
How pitiful
that my Foundation Building Liquid is wasted.

140
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,230
How could they say that?

141
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,640
Students these days…

142
00:07:48,790 --> 00:07:49,630
Elder.

143
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:01,620
(Elders' House)

144
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,880
Elder Hao, what's wrong?

145
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:18,160
Students nowadays…

146
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,110
Some students are claiming that

147
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,230
Xiao Yan should return
the Fallen Heart Flame.

148
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,790
They don't even care about my liquid.

149
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,920
What're you angry at?

150
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:34,280
Returning the Fallen Heart Flame,

151
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,550
or your liquid?

152
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,120
You!

153
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:39,400
You're annoying.

154
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,670
That's a Grade II elixir!

155
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,350
You're an elder.

156
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:45,110
How come you can't discipline students?

157
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:49,200
He's not an ordinary student.

158
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,320
You mean

159
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,120
Bai Cheng.

160
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:58,440
Demanding the return of the Flame

161
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:01,350
is a clear sign of targeting Xiao Yan.

162
00:09:10,110 --> 00:09:11,110
What happened?

163
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:12,430
No idea.

164
00:09:13,350 --> 00:09:14,190
Dear classmates,

165
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,320
the Bai Group is established today.

166
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,790
I believe many of you are well aware

167
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:21,790
some people in Inner Academy

168
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,550
purport to be heroes,

169
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:27,440
but rely on their size and strength

170
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,760
to seize resources for their own use.

171
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,400
They selfishly improve themselves

172
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,030
regardless of the interests of others.

173
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,280
That equals cheating.

174
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:38,760
I don't mind you founding the group,

175
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,080
but why are you smearing Xiao Yan?

176
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,880
Did I say it's Xiao Yan?

177
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:45,590
The only reason you're eager for defense

178
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,000
is because you feel guilty.

179
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:50,080
- I'm not guilty.
- Besides,

180
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:52,520
Xiao Yan took the Fallen Heart Flame away.

181
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,440
Is it a slander?

182
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,670
It's a fact.

183
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,640
I, Bai Cheng, promise that

184
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,150
I will never befriend Xiao Yan.

185
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,640
All members of my group

186
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,230
have access to

187
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:07,400
all the skills I have acquired

188
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,760
and all the elixirs.

189
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,840
Bai Group.

190
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:18,200
Bai Group. Bai Group. Bai Group.

191
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:19,150
Bai Group.

192
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:23,320
Bai Group. Bai Group. Bai Group.

193
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:27,320
Bai Group. Bai Group. Bai Group.

194
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:33,550
Bai Group. Bai Group. Bai Group.

195
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,200
Everyone,

196
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,710
hadn't Xiao Yan conquered the Fallen Heart Flame,

197
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,520
Jia Nan Academy would have disappeared.

198
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:43,080
Bai Group

199
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:45,110
will retake the Academy possessions

200
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:46,880
and stand against Xiao Yan.

201
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,920
Bai Cheng,

202
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:51,110
did you get the approval of the Guard
before establishment?

203
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,960
No wonder Xiao Yan is so arrogant.

204
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:56,310
Has he bribed the Guard?

205
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,120
What?

206
00:10:58,590 --> 00:10:59,790
You're a small guard leader.

207
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,470
Do you want to control Academy rules?

208
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,240
Let's see

209
00:11:04,590 --> 00:11:06,280
whether you can change the rules.

210
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,160
Wu Hao.

211
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:08,630
Headmaster.

212
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,160
Bai Cheng,

213
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:21,000
your Bai Group should take responsibility.

214
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,120
Why are you

215
00:11:23,710 --> 00:11:24,550
doing this?

216
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:26,480
Headmaster,

217
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:27,720
I'm doing this

218
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:29,350
for the students of Inner Academy

219
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:30,550
to take back our possessions.

220
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,640
Your possessions.

221
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:35,280
What do you mean?

222
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:37,150
The Fallen Heart Flame,

223
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,080
the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower,

224
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,590
or the whole academy?

225
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,040
Students,

226
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,320
it was not because of luck

227
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,670
that Xiao Yan conquered the Fallen Heart Flame.

228
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:54,710
At a dangerous moment,

229
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:56,520
he stepped out for the academy.

230
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,440
Our academy is set for practice.

231
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,000
Every graduate

232
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:06,110
has decency and moral ethics.

233
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:09,150
Without such realization,

234
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:11,080
I think you'd better

235
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,150
be dismissed from the Academy.

236
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:17,760
Well, well, that's it.

237
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,080
Clear off. Take your class.

238
00:12:19,610 --> 00:12:20,500
Go.

239
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,360
Let's go. Go.

240
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,360
Headmaster,

241
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,710
does my brother deserve to die?

242
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:29,230
I've told you everything.

243
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,280
Now that you're so overwhelmed,

244
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:32,720
fine,

245
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:35,150
you're granted permission
to access the Refining Tower

246
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,110
for practicing.

247
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:39,000
But, think it through.

248
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:42,200
Are you confining me and my Bai Group?

249
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:47,030
I said it's for practicing.

250
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,590
If you regard it as confinement,

251
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,470
then it is.

252
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:01,030
Go, go.

253
00:13:27,110 --> 00:13:27,950
Gu Yao,

254
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,960
you know I value you.

255
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:32,760
You should be aware

256
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:35,110
I have great hope for you.

257
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,240
Mr. Gu,

258
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:39,030
are you worried about Hall of Souls?

259
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:42,350
The Bodhisattva Tree sealing Hun Miesheng

260
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,590
is not in a stable condition.

261
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,440
Although it's guided
by the Black Submerged Army,

262
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:47,550
I just can't

263
00:13:48,110 --> 00:13:48,950
rest assured.

264
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:51,320
Hun Miesheng

265
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,880
was the trump of the Hall of Souls.

266
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:57,320
As Mu Gu now claims to be the Master,

267
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,670
he must have some wrong ideas.

268
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:02,200
You need to inspect it.

269
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,880
Strength the seal if it's safe.

270
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:07,350
Report immediately

271
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:08,750
if it's not.

272
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,880
I'll do whatever I can.

273
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:13,760
It's our mission to suppress evil forces.

274
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:17,520
Remember to keep a low profile.

275
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,640
Don't draw attention,

276
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:23,470
or cause avoidable panic in Central Plains.

277
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,520
Pick some followers from the Army

278
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,920
and start your task.

279
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,070
Mr. Gu,

280
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,920
I have a request

281
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,280
for the followers.

282
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
Please grant my request.

283
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:45,080
Miss, Mr. Gu orders you to leave the altar

284
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,000
and take on a task.

285
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,710
Why does he change his mind suddenly?

