00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,230
From what I know,

287
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,000
you're asked to assist the Black Submerged Army.

288
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:56,470
I knew Gu Yao would get me out.

289
00:15:12,710 --> 00:15:13,960
Dad.

290
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:21,350
Have you reflected on yourself these days?

291
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,150
Since I'm back,

292
00:15:24,350 --> 00:15:26,030
I will prioritize the whole clan.

293
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,520
Go check the seal that confines Hun Miesheng

294
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,910
together with Gu Yao.

295
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:32,520
It's of great importance.

296
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,800
Don't joke around.

297
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:37,640
But for the request of Gu Yao,

298
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:39,590
by no means will I

299
00:15:39,590 --> 00:15:41,470
allow you to leave the altar.

300
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,150
I know clearly

301
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,400
what you are thinking of.

302
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,470
If this time

303
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,960
you fail at the task for other things,

304
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,350
I will punish both of you.

305
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:53,720
I would bear the punishment

306
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,880
if we failed this time.

307
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,440
I will finish the task.

308
00:15:59,150 --> 00:15:59,990
Just go.

309
00:16:05,280 --> 00:16:06,120
Wait a second.

310
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:20,910
Inspect secretly.

311
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:22,320
Don't stick your neck out.

312
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,360
Remember,

313
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:27,110
you're the only Clan Lady of our Clan.

314
00:16:28,110 --> 00:16:28,950
Dad, don't worry.

315
00:16:29,350 --> 00:16:30,840
I will come back safely.

316
00:16:31,880 --> 00:16:34,230
I will definitely prioritize her safety.

317
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:38,990
Go ahead.

318
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,480
Slow down.

319
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,600
Sit down.

320
00:17:01,710 --> 00:17:02,880
Have a rest in my room now.

321
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:04,430
I'm going to find the headmaster.

322
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,680
He will save you.

323
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,950
Xiao Yan, please be quick.

324
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:15,760
She can't make it to this noon.

325
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:17,550
OK.

326
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:29,110
Another petition from the students.

327
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:29,950
Yeah.

328
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:30,910
Bai Cheng,

329
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:33,470
using the Fallen Heart Flame as an excuse,

330
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,950
challenges the Academy

331
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:37,040
and incites

332
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,310
dissatisfaction with Xiao Yan and the Academy.

333
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:40,640
He's forcing the Academy

334
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:41,950
to ask Xiao Yan

335
00:17:42,430 --> 00:17:44,430
to return the Fallen Heart Flame.

336
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,880
Bai Cheng

337
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:47,760
has great popularity among students.

338
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:52,040
Everyone admires and respects him.

339
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,680
He airs his voice,

340
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,430
and students

341
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:58,830
naturally, follow him.

342
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,430
Now he's on lockdown,

343
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,280
students are

344
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:03,600
even more dissatisfied.

345
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,280
Headmaster, Elder Hu Qian,

346
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:07,840
I'm back.

347
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:12,230
Xiao Yan, you come at the right time.

348
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:15,070
Are you returning the Fallen Heart Flame?

349
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:20,880
What?

350
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:22,590
Anything else?

351
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,350
Years ago in the Magic Beast Mountain Range,

352
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,190
I met a friend named Little Fairy Doctor.

353
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,950
She was exploited by Han Feng
because of her Woeful Poison Body.

354
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:32,430
When we met again in the Demon Flame Valley,

355
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:35,280
I promised her to find her an antidote,

356
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:36,950
so

357
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:39,190
I want to ask

358
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,070
if it's possible to let my friend enter

359
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:42,520
the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower
for isolation,

360
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,000
so that I'll have some time

361
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:47,070
to find the Bodhisattva Saliva
that can neutralize the poison body.

362
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,920
Woeful Poison Body.

363
00:18:52,710 --> 00:18:55,160
Is it congenital

364
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,110
or acquired?

365
00:18:58,800 --> 00:18:59,640
She was born with it.

366
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:05,880
Congenital Woeful Poison Body
is powerful and hard-to-control.

367
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,800
When it's out of control,

368
00:19:09,430 --> 00:19:11,880
the poison will erupt,
and the toxic gas will spread,

369
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,760
causing

370
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,680
devastation.

371
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:18,280
But she has been desperately restraining it

372
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:19,920
and persisted all the way
to the Jia Nan Academy.

373
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,680
I know that the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower

374
00:19:22,950 --> 00:19:24,400
used to be a place for storing Fallen Heart Flame

375
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,160
and is an isolated location.

376
00:19:26,760 --> 00:19:28,590
So, if given some time,

377
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,880
I can find the Bodhisattva Saliva,

378
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:32,800
and let her safely live out her life.

379
00:19:33,470 --> 00:19:34,310
Shut up!

380
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,560
The Woeful Poison Body is a curse!

381
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:41,350
When she can't control it and it erupts,

382
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:44,000
the entire Academy and even the Jia Ma Empire

383
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,230
will suffer devastating blows.

384
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:47,760
Headmaster…

385
00:19:47,950 --> 00:19:48,880
You know that

386
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:50,760
I value your talent

387
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:53,000
and I know you bear a heavy responsibility,

388
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:56,070
so I repeatedly tolerated you and helped you.

389
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:59,430
But do you think you can act recklessly?

390
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:00,780
I wouldn't dare.

391
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,110
You are still young.

392
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:05,830
Do you think that

393
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,470
by achieving everything,

394
00:20:09,950 --> 00:20:11,640
you can disregard this world

395
00:20:11,760 --> 00:20:13,160
and all the lives here?

396
00:20:16,710 --> 00:20:17,830
Little do you know that

397
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
there are things

398
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,040
in this world that you cannot reverse.

399
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,830
Jia Nan Academy

400
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,920
has bottom lines.

401
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:38,350
There's no room for negotiation.

402
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,400
Bring your friend

403
00:20:41,230 --> 00:20:42,070
out of here!

404
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:44,520
Headmaster.

405
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:47,360
Headmaster.

406
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:48,720
Headmaster.

407
00:21:09,430 --> 00:21:10,270
Hey,

408
00:21:10,280 --> 00:21:11,120
Xiao Yan.

409
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,400
Xiao Yan.

410
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:13,880
Xiao Yan.

411
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:15,640
Elder Hu Qian.

412
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:19,840
What's wrong, Elder?

413
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:22,430
Xiao Yan,

414
00:21:23,470 --> 00:21:24,950
please don't blame the Headmaster.

415
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:29,160
When he received his education here,

416
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:30,430
he had a friend

417
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:32,680
born with a Woeful Poison Body.

418
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,760
He scoured Ja Ma Empire

419
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:38,680
for a drop of Bodhisattva Saliva.

420
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:41,880
And what's the result?

421
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,760
Bodhisattva trees in Ja Ma Empire

422
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,190
had perished long ago.

423
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:48,680
The whole Dou Qi Continent

424
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:51,400
produced no Bodhisattva Saliva.

425
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:53,600
So,

426
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,560
what about his friend?

427
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:58,830
Without antidotes,

428
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,040
the Poison Body broke out.

429
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:05,040
All lands were poisoned overnight.

430
00:22:10,430 --> 00:22:11,270
Headmaster

431
00:22:11,590 --> 00:22:14,470
had to take his friend to a remote mountain.

432
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:18,590
Three days later,

433
00:22:20,110 --> 00:22:22,070
he came back alone,

434
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:24,160
full of grief.

435
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,000
Since then,

436
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:30,400
no one has talked about the incident.

437
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:32,520
It took him

438
00:22:33,070 --> 00:22:35,040
a whole decade of effort

439
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:36,950
to clear up the toxin inside his body.

440
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,000
You can imagine

441
00:22:41,190 --> 00:22:42,350
how miserable it was

442
00:22:44,190 --> 00:22:45,430
in the remote mountain.

443
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:55,070
He just fears you repeat the history.

444
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:58,430
Being poisoned is secondary

445
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:01,110
to letting friends down.

446
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:05,040
It's unbearably painful

447
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:07,950
for ordinary people

448
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,190
to kill friends by themselves.

449
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:14,760
Headmaster has done everything to help you.

450
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:17,520
Bai Cheng abetted students against you

451
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:19,470
and caused trouble in the Academy.

452
00:23:20,230 --> 00:23:21,800
Headmaster has been on your side.

453
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:26,400
Don't blame him for being ruthless.

454
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,070
Don't enter the tower on your own.

455
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:32,280
Bai Cheng is confined there.

456
00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:37,150
I won't.

457
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:47,800
If my poison becomes active,

458
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,040
please don't show mercy to me.

459
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:53,360
Rest assured.

460
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:55,150
In that case,

461
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,070
I would take you to the underground

462
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,160
without letting you poison the Academy.

463
00:24:03,710 --> 00:24:05,230
Although you look brutal,

464
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,430
you always consider Xiao Yan's benefits.

465
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,590
How lucky he is

466
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:13,110
to have such a friend like you.

467
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,000
It's 12 o'clock.

468
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:24,310
Where's he? He's so slow.

469
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,110
Any progress? Can she enter the tower?

470
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:38,230
Headmaster refused my request.

471
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:43,600
Little Fairy Doctor,

472
00:24:45,710 --> 00:24:46,550
I'm sorry.

473
00:24:48,710 --> 00:24:49,560
No need to.

474
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,400
I knew I shouldn't come here.

475
00:24:53,710 --> 00:24:54,590
Don't feel sorry.

476
00:24:55,520 --> 00:24:56,430
If you're not accepted here,

477
00:24:57,110 --> 00:24:58,110
let's come back to Serpent Kingdom with me.

478
00:24:59,000 --> 00:24:59,840
I don't believe

479
00:24:59,950 --> 00:25:01,830
only Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower

480
00:25:01,830 --> 00:25:02,880
can prevent it from breaking out.

481
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:07,670
Little Fairy Doctor,

482
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:10,680
your face…

483
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,480
Don't worry.

484
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:19,350
We will find solutions.

485
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:26,310
Xiao Yan is back.

486
00:25:27,230 --> 00:25:29,310
Xiao Yan. Xiao Yan.

487
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,190
Xiao Yan.

488
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:33,560
You're really here.

489
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:35,880
We're leaving.

490
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:37,190
No.

491
00:25:37,470 --> 00:25:38,880
You're just back here.

492
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,190
I refuse.

493
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,240
If we stay here,

494
00:25:42,470 --> 00:25:43,470
you will die.

495
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:02,350
She's such a beautiful girl,

496
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:05,040
yet with such a pitiful life.

497
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:08,430
Don't worry.

498
00:26:08,710 --> 00:26:10,470
I will handle this matter.

499
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:12,310
How can you handle it?

500
00:26:13,470 --> 00:26:15,000
Headmaster refused to help us.

501
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,190
What can you do?

502
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:18,880
You want to enter the tower, right?

503
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:21,000
I'm on it.

504
00:26:32,470 --> 00:26:33,310
Elder Hao,

505
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,070
why are you on their side?

506
00:26:38,590 --> 00:26:39,710
Hu Jia has told me everything.

507
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:41,560
In my 30-year teaching career,

508
00:26:41,830 --> 00:26:43,950
this is the first Woeful Poison Body I've seen.

509
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:48,160
Such a precious sample must be preserved.

510
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,830
Elder Hao, she's not a sample.

511
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:56,070
I… It's just a metaphor.

512
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:59,230
I mean I can try my best

513
00:27:00,070 --> 00:27:01,190
to keep her poison under control.

514
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:02,920
To show my sincerity,

515
00:27:03,230 --> 00:27:04,400
I'd like to enter the tower with her.

516
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,470
Headmaster's order.

517
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:33,310
Bai Group

518
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:36,680
has been confined for ten days.

519
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:38,150
Now,

520
00:27:38,430 --> 00:27:41,160
you can leave
the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower.

521
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:45,950
Bai Cheng.

522
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:49,070
Unless Xiao Yan goes with me,

523
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,710
I won't leave the tower.

524
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,120
Brother Bai Cheng,

525
00:27:54,470 --> 00:27:55,310
I'm Xiao Yan.

526
00:27:55,950 --> 00:27:58,160
Elder Hu Qian fabricated the order for you,

527
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:01,160
which means Headmaster refused your request.

528
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,430
As that's the case,

529
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,040
I, a punished student,

530
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:09,160
have no reason to help you.

531
00:28:10,110 --> 00:28:12,430
I'd like to take all punishments.

532
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,110
I can get out of the tower,

533
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,830
but you can't enter it.

534
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,240
You're at my disposal.

535
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:25,640
As long as Little Fairy Doctor enters,

536
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:27,680
I'm at your disposal.

537
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:29,600
Good.

538
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,240
Xiao Yan,

539
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:42,950
thanks.

540
00:28:47,070 --> 00:28:48,520
This is where my life ends.

541
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:50,840
It's not.

542
00:28:51,430 --> 00:28:52,270
Let's go.

543
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,000
This way.

544
00:29:22,350 --> 00:29:23,190
What's wrong?

545
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:25,360
Watch out.

546
00:30:10,310 --> 00:30:11,150
Wu Hao.

547
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:16,910
Open your mouth.

548
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:18,400
Wake up.

549
00:30:20,430 --> 00:30:21,270
Wake up.

550
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:24,190
Don't look at her.

551
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,240
Otherwise, you're over.

552
00:30:28,560 --> 00:30:29,400
Xiao Yan

553
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,470
is just so lucky.

554
00:30:31,950 --> 00:30:33,040
He has met all kinds of people

555
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,470
others could never meet in their lifetime.

556
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,040
Besides the Woeful Poison Body,

557
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:40,230
there's the Triple Jade-Green Snake Flower Pupils.

558
00:30:40,470 --> 00:30:41,520
Triple Jade-Green Snake Flower Pupils?

559
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,230
It means in her eyes,

560
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:47,310
three flowers appear at the same time.

561
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,920
Even an advanced Dou Ancestor

562
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:51,000
would lose all the power.

563
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,000
Everyone

564
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,680
would fall into the illusion.

565
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:55,790
Sleep.

566
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,310
Avoid her eyes!

567
00:31:08,760 --> 00:31:09,880
Split up! Go!

568
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:21,760
Your Highness.

569
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,310
Little Fairy Doctor. You!

570
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,190
Little Fairy Doctor.

571
00:31:58,230 --> 00:31:59,070
Your face…

572
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:05,310
Is my face darker?

573
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,760
Little Fairy Doctor,

574
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,470
